title:
Foxconn's Young Liu Meets with NVIDIA's Jensen Huang, Forecasts to Announce 
News at Computex Taipei
text: Young Liu, Chairman of Foxconn, attended NVIDIA Corporation (NVDA.US)      's GTC. After visiting Foxconn's exhibition area with Jensen Huang, NVIDIA Corporation's CEO, Liu said that the content of the interaction between the two companies will be released at the Computex Taipei to be held in June.(Real-time Streaming US Stocks Quote; Except All OTC quotes are at least 15 minutes delayed.)Related NewsInitial Jobless Claims in United States for Mar/23 is 210K, Below ForecastAAStocks Financial News
